%N A015488 Inverse of 1479th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015488 Periodic with period length 1479. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015488 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015488/b015488.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015488 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1479.
%H A015488 <a href="/index/Rec#order_896">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 896.
